Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The furthest space city from Earth,\Nknown as Side 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...proclaimed itself the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In roughly one month of fighting,\Nthe Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Federation Forces caused\Nthe deaths of half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The war became a stalemate,\Nand eight months have now passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam Rising!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Slender, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The military facilities appear\Nto be in the upper right block, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be rush hour,\Nbut I see only one car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a person in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He hasn't even eaten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd find you cooped up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to eat your breakfast...\NYou should take better care of your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Amuro!\NHello, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of energy as always, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you planning on wearing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat after I finish rewiring this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear the evacuation order?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuation order?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what the siren was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you listen to the military broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A warship's docking so we have to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, we don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right.\N- Evacuate at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside. Come on, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're Amuro's closest neighbor!\NIt was your responsibility to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, about the evacuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. He's all alone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if military engineers like his dad\Nhadn't moved here in the first place, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still bitter about them moving us\Nto make way for their research facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming! Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's bad manners to eat and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your father on the incoming ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. He said he was going\NEarthside about a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they'll be fighting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He wouldn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Gundam components\Nloaded onto the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Speed up the ground operations.\N- Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn the White Base!\NThey're leading a Zeon ship here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- So this is it?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation has a fine new battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With this new ship,\Nand the completed Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll have no trouble crushing Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lieutenant Ray.\NWe're docking at Side 7 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the bridge at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Bright, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir.\N- How many months in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Six months, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you're 19 years old, correct?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When we start mass-producing the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...we may be able to end this war without\Nsending kids like you into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your son, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there are kids his age\Nfighting as guerrilla soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm told that it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, Lieutenant Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So we weren't able to outrun that Zeon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I don't have much luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To run into a prize like that\Non my way home from a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were the lucky ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lt. Commander Char. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the Federation's Operation V really\Nbe based in a remote Side like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be developing a more\Nadvanced mobile suit than our Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Not in such a remote place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Code CC2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Exactly as I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Federation\Nhas mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We should assume their development\Nwas successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The third one's a mobile suit as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be more in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just here on recon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they get those mobile suits\Nloaded onto that battleship...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty to seek your glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gene, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at Lt. Commander Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...he built his career on actual combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gene?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize this is insubordination?!\NCease and desist, Gene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to care, after I pull this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner you defeat the enemy, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's an asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The way these tremors are traveling,\Nthey must be caused by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Zeons. A Zeon attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll go find my father.\N- Amuro, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Going out could put us all in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's with the military.\NA shelter like this won't survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to request an evacuation\Nto the ship that just docked today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please close the other door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Zeon mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a Zeon Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Civilians must remain in the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for an engineering officer\Nnamed Tem Ray. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably on the ship...\NUnload it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Classified Materials"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This must be...\Nthe Federation's mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was following orders, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's Chief Denim?\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's moved forward, to support Gene.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Federation has mobile suits there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Slender, take as many pictures as you can...\Nand retreat if it becomes dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that Denim\Ncouldn't control a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have to go out there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take us closer to Side 7.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the space port! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Faster!\N- Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Computer-controlled operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A learning type computer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! No wonder Dad's been preoccupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Use one of the inner lifts for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get to the space port, Fraw!\N- Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw! Hurry up!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about Lift #3?\N- It's being used by the evacuees!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam must go before the evacuees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take it up to the White Base\Nand prepare it for battle.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, why aren't you evacuating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, are mobile suits more\Nimportant to you than human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move it out.\N- Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up to the White Base, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the warship that's in port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine won't start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the White Base.\NI'll go find a tractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the Federation's secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw... Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother? Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw, they'll get you too. You've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!\NYou're stronger than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a run for the space port.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, right, Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there soon. Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Fraw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Fraw Bow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This will work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same. Is this it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy gain is more than five times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Left... and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base!\NCan't you launch a Core Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless we blast open the Side's hull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we deployed all combat personnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! And we've also sent pilots\Nto retrieve the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We never expected an attack\Nfrom within the colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Denim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's mobile suit has moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were all\Njust unassembled parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not functioning very well.\NI'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This mobile suit is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rifles are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch, you damn Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just on a recon mission!\NRetreat, Gene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!\NIf we don't get him now, the enemy will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, one of our mobile suits is operating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of attack is that?!\NWho's in the cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I'm out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!\NNo matter how thick your armor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the mobile suit's shaking in terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of\Nthe Federation's mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this thing have any other weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gene, can you jump to where Slender is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the back-up camera. I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hit the mobile suit's engine,\Nit might destroy all of Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for what you did to Gene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do...\NCan I target just the cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If this Zaku blows up, all the air\Nin Side 7 will be sucked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rush the civilians onto the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any more air is escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And the transfer of the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All the regular engineers were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll have him do it.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's a real pilot or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...we need his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Slender?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's escaped Side 7\Nand is headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No one likes to admit to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To the mistakes they've made\Nbecause of their youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As Char waits for the White Base\Nto escape from Side 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...he shows his true power as the Red Comet,\Nand faces Gundam with brutal force.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For both Char and Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...this battle reveals a ferocity\Nthat neither has experienced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:54.07,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:54.07,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:59.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:59.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:09.30,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:09.30,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:14.22,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:14.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.85,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.85,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.23,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:28.82,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:28.82,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:39.12,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:39.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
